query: select top(1) PerC.UniqueId, PerC.LastName + ' ' + PerC.FirstName + ' ' + PerC.MiddleName Ent, PerC.LastName LN, PerC.FirstName FN, PerC.MiddleName MN from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.LastName not like '%[a-zA-Z0-9]%' and len(PerC.LastName) > 0 and len(PerC.UniqueId) = (select min(len(PerC.UniqueId)) from PersonCards PerC)

select top(1) PerC.UniqueId, PerC.LastName + ' ' + PerC.FirstName + ' ' + PerC.MiddleName Ent, PerC.LastName LN, PerC.FirstName FN, PerC.MiddleName MN from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.LastName not like '%[a-zA-Z0-9]%' and len(PerC.LastName) > 0 and len(PerC.UniqueId) = (select max(len(PerC.UniqueId)) from PersonCards PerC)
